Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mother clears her throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,let me be perfectly clear - Mouthface, cover your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What???
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuuh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you see that girl right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I made her. Out of my blood and my flesh, my sweat and my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love her more than the waking world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will smother her in her sleep, before I see her ruin herself with some - thing like you, so you better just run along now, because you'd have better luck sticking your pecker in a cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Mouthface, mom is done, come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, well -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to be friendly, like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's war between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear: One way or another, I'm gonna have that daughter of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You better keep one eye open, cause you just made an enemy of - the Bandit King!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Cletus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Saddle up!
